{"text_id":27144,"tokens":["Acknowledge"," your"," emotions",".:"," The"," first"," step"," to"," getting"," over"," being"," rejected"," from"," a"," job"," is"," to"," acknowledge"," your"," emotions","."," It","'","s"," okay"," to"," feel"," sad",","," angry",","," or"," discouraged","."," Allow"," yourself"," to"," feel"," these"," emotions"," and"," recognize"," that"," they"," are"," a"," normal"," part"," of"," the"," process",".","\n\n","Talk"," to"," a"," friend"," or"," family"," member"," about"," what"," you"," are"," going"," through",".:"," Sharing"," your"," feelings"," with"," someone"," you"," trust"," can"," help"," you"," feel"," better","."," Talk"," to"," a"," friend"," or"," family"," member"," about"," your"," experience"," and"," how"," you"," are"," feeling","."," They"," may"," be"," able"," to"," offer"," you"," some"," perspective"," or"," advice"," that"," will"," help"," you"," move"," forward",".","\n\n","Dist","ract"," yourself"," from"," dwelling"," on"," your"," rejection",".:"," While"," it","'","s"," important"," to"," acknowledge"," your"," emotions",","," you"," don","'","t"," want"," to"," dwell"," on"," your"," rejection","."," Find"," ways"," to"," distract"," yourself",","," such"," as"," by"," pursuing"," a"," hobby",","," spending"," time"," with"," friends",","," or"," engaging"," in"," a"," fun"," activity",".","\n\n","Think"," positively",".:"," Try"," to"," focus"," on"," the"," positive"," aspects"," of"," your"," job"," search","."," Instead"," of"," dwelling"," on"," the"," rejection",","," think"," about"," the"," opportunities"," that"," are"," still"," available"," to"," you","."," Keep"," a"," positive"," attitude"," and"," stay"," motivated",".","\n\n","Read"," biographies"," and"," autobio","graphies"," that"," will"," motivate"," you",".:"," Reading"," about"," the"," successes"," of"," others"," can"," be"," a"," great"," way"," to"," stay"," motivated","."," Look"," for"," biographies"," and"," autobio","graphies"," that"," will"," inspire"," you"," and"," help"," you"," stay"," focused"," on"," your"," goals",".","\n\n","Speak"," to"," a"," therapist"," as"," a"," last"," resort"," if"," you"," are"," having"," a"," hard"," time"," processing"," your"," emotions",".:"," If"," you"," are"," having"," a"," hard"," time"," processing"," your"," emotions"," and"," moving"," on"," from"," the"," rejection",","," consider"," speaking"," to"," a"," therapist","."," They"," can"," provide"," you"," with"," the"," support"," and"," guidance"," you"," need"," to"," work"," through"," your"," feelings",".","\n\n","Manage"," the"," stress"," caused"," by"," getting"," rejected",".:"," Rejection"," can"," be"," stressful",","," so"," it","'","s"," important"," to"," find"," ways"," to"," manage"," that"," stress","."," Try"," techniques"," such"," as"," deep"," breathing",","," meditation",","," or"," yoga"," to"," help"," you"," relax",".","\n\n","Get"," plenty"," of"," exercise",".:"," Exercise"," is"," a"," great"," way"," to"," reduce"," stress"," and"," improve"," your"," mood","."," Make"," sure"," to"," get"," plenty"," of"," physical"," activity"," each"," day",".","\n\n","Spend"," some"," time"," doing"," yoga",".:"," Yoga"," is"," a"," great"," way"," to"," reduce"," stress"," and"," improve"," your"," mental"," and"," physical"," well","-","being","."," Spend"," some"," time"," each"," day"," doing"," yoga"," to"," help"," you"," relax"," and"," move"," on"," from"," the"," rejection",".","\n\n","Practice"," meditation",".:"," Meditation"," can"," help"," you"," clear"," your"," mind"," and"," focus"," on"," the"," present"," moment","."," Practice"," meditation"," each"," day"," to"," help"," you"," stay"," calm"," and"," centered","."],"sub_source":"wikihow","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}